<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>تحديث حالة المستشفى</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Cairo', 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e3f0ff 0%, #f9f9f9 100%);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #222;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 430px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 18px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            padding: 36px 32px 28px 32px;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #0077b6;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            font-size: 2rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 22px;
        }
        .form-group, fieldset {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        label {
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
            color: #333;
        }
        select, input[type="number"] {
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border: 1px solid #cfd8dc;
            border-radius: 7px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            background: #f7fbff;
            transition: border 0.2s;
        }
        select:focus, input[type="number"]:focus {
            border-color: #0077b6;
            outline: none;
            background: #e3f0ff;
        }
        fieldset {
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px 14px 10px 14px;
            margin: 0;
            background: #f8fafc;
        }
        legend {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: #0077b6;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0 8px;
        }
        .beds-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .beds-row input[type="number"] {
            width: 90px;
        }
        button[type="submit"] {
            margin-top: 18px;
            padding: 12px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0077b6 60%, #00b4d8 100%);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 7px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,123,182,0.08);
        }
        button[type="submit"]:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #005f87 60%, #0096c7 100%);
        }
        .back-link {
            display: block;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 22px;
            color: #0077b6;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }
        .back-link:hover {
            color: #023e8a;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 18px 6vw 18px 6vw;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }
        }
        .note {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>تحديث حالة المستشفى</h1>
        <div class="note">يرجى تحديث حالة الطوارئ وعدد الأسرة المتاحة بدقة.</div>
        <form action="/api/hospitals/status" method="POST" class="form" autocomplete="off">
            <input type="hidden" name="_method" value="PUT">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="er-available">جاهزية قسم الطوارئ</label>
                <select name="isERAvailable" id="er-available" required>
                    <option value="" disabled selected>اختر الحالة</option>
                    <option value="true">متاح</option>
                    <option value="false">غير متاح</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <fieldset>
                <legend>عدد الأسرة المتاحة</legend>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="icuTotal">العناية المركزة (ICU):</label>
                    <div class="beds-row">
                        <input type="number" id="icuTotal" name="availableBeds[ICU][total]" placeholder="الإجمالي" min="0" required>
                        <input type="number" name="availableBeds[ICU][occupied]" placeholder="المشغول" min="0" required>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="erTotal">الطوارئ:</label>
                    <div class="beds-row">
                        <input type="number" id="erTotal" name="availableBeds[emergency][total]" placeholder="الإجمالي" min="0" required>
                        <input type="number" name="availableBeds[emergency][occupied]" placeholder="المشغول" min="0" required>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </fieldset>
            <button type="submit">تحديث الحالة</button>
        </form>
        <a href="/hospital-panel/dashboard" class="back-link">العودة إلى لوحة التحكم</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>